{"tid":415052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三跑融資690億 公眾可認購50億零售債券","createTime":"2017-09-26T16:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T18:59:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a3fab29b354bba2472e0c7a182b779aef3fec32a","tid":415052,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"機管局耗資1,415億元推行機場三跑工程，計劃透過徵收機場建設費、港府停收股息，以及向市場舉債融資。機管局去年委聘滙豐銀行為財務顧問，研究可行融資方法，本月完成研究。根據該局最新提交立法會－滙豐在顧問報告－的總結，有信心機管局可透過舉債，可籌集690億元新貸款應付工程資金，建議透過多種方法發債，包括發行為期3年，規模約50億元的零售債券供公眾認購，以增加公眾對三跑項目的參與。<br />\n<br />\n機管局提交立法會的文件指，滙豐銀行在報告建議的詳細融資方案分3部分，建議在18/19財政年度上半年先做準備工作；下半年開始短期融資活動，包括向機構投資者先發行10年債券，及50億元的零售債券，同時擴大現時的50億港元銀行循環貸款，至最高100億港元，應付流動資金需求。到20/21年度至三跑竣工，則建議按市況及開支狀況融資，包括向銀行取得5年期的貸款，貸款總額或達最高200億至300億港元；另外，同時再向機構投資者發行年期較短，約5至7年期的美元或其他外幣債券，發行規模最高為290億港元，部分債券建議用「綠色債券」方式包裝。<br />\n機管局指，接照計劃1,415億元建造成本中，260億元來自收取機場建設費、470億來自政府停收股息的營運盈餘，餘下690億則為新增貸款。該局強調，滙豐有信心機管局能以合理條款籌集690億資金，而目前的融資方案屬穩健可行。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170926/large/1506418501_d3b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170926%2Flarge%2F1506418501_d3b2.jpg&h=63efe4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場第三條跑道（箭嘴示）；機管局早前決定經融資方式，不經立法會財委會撥款，興建機場第三條跑道；圖為三跑設計圖片。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170926/57258464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170926%2F57258464&d=xGs9AEHpjal4PHFOuyzWgTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a002d648\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170926%2F57258464&h=9c7844ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170926/57258464</a>"},{"pid":"941e76307a295a387c379d908664ce2ffba809f9","tid":415052,"uid":56624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"等睇機管局破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ed5be3017f321fca4c61185a3c520492dbf7bd","tid":415052,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"買唔買得過"},{"pid":"049070306558bbba86fa1bd73bfd4c304db62cb1","tid":415052,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"1400億跑道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齋降不升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ceee252e4f3c73cc539c6279a2b38eb2dac0c9","tid":415052,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:38:53.000Z","msg":"頂盡2厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5f047497e7dcb527700993b90662113a8f2917","tid":415052,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"一定超資<br />\n<br />\n起火箭都唔洗咁貴"},{"pid":"ff6f4a3a5aa50faea570c5c999bd5205c660cc09","tid":415052,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"1da281fc4890936bbc3caac4e7f928e7fb117063","tid":415052,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"肯定冇肉食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13b0bee7ae5cb66cac02460ee294ea291b99601","tid":415052,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戇鳩鳩<br />\n咁似大陸蝕到仆街個個咩鐵路部既"},{"pid":"a58148ea666eca02053d7bc796f826480d071619","tid":415052,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戇鳩鳩<br />\n咁似大陸蝕到仆街個個咩鐵路部既</blockquote><br />\n擺明做同一樣嘢啦"},{"pid":"57b53baa3e93710ee6290b630e3a774138ebc65f","tid":415052,"